You can put the IMDB dataset on folder named data on project root or application will downloaded it;
This application use DuckDB for analyzing the TSV.GZ files and creating reports.

Also application use Actuator plugin for extracting metrics like http.server.request
so you can get metrics by calling api
GET /actuator/metrics/http.server.requests
on "statistic" key you can found number of count like "statistic":"COUNT","value":1.0

You can get API usage from http://localhost:8080/swagger-ui/index.html

